title: 61. The ✨Acne✨ Purge (And Other Lessons I Didn't Learn in Esthetician School.)
description: Hi Roomies!! I'm back with a solo ep sharing the major lessons I didn't learn in esthetician school... aka things I've learned the hard way in the "real world" as an esthetician.  Have a topic request or question for a future episode? Comment on my latest @myestytessa.
